Tempdb :
Copy code

mkfs.xfs /dev/vg_tempdb/lv_sybasetmp
1️⃣1️⃣ Monter filesystem
Copy code

mount /dev/vg_dump/lv_sybase_dump /apps/sybase/dump/ESY3_FR_UAT_ASE
mount /dev/vg_tempdb/lv_sybasetmp /apps/sybasetmp/ESY3_FR_UAT_ASE
1️⃣2️⃣ Ajouter fstab
Copy code

/dev/vg_dump/lv_sybase_dump   /apps/sybase/dump/ESY3_FR_UAT_ASE   xfs  defaults,noatime  0 0
/dev/vg_tempdb/lv_sybasetmp   /apps/sybasetmp/ESY3_FR_UAT_ASE     xfs  defaults,noatime  0 0
